    "Some audio transformation techniques can be applied to increase the number of training samples, such as pitch variation, and noise injection.",
    "The raw audio and transformed audio are scale invariant.",
    "Then, we generate the log-Mel spectrogram (x i, x j) from the raw and augmented sequence.",
    "The encoder network obtains the discriminate features (h i, h j).",
    "Next, we construct the projection head to obtain representative features (z i, z j)."
